    body: `Generate quotes and invoices in GetSign: (1) Install GetSign and open an item view. (2) Click Upload a New Template to add an invoice/quote in PDF or DOCX, or create one within GetSign; map relevant board columns (email, files, status) for real-time updates. (3) Toggle on GetSign Generate. (4) Configure line items: drag the Line Items field to the template, then tap Configure Line Item to select which subitem columns display (product name, quantity, unit price, discount). Subitems act as detailed line items with automatic totals and taxes. (5) Review fields and signature requirements, then Send via email or copy the sharing link; recipients can view, sign, and approve immediately, and status updates automatically. Capabilities: automatic calculations for totals, taxes, and credits; reusable templates; real-time status tracking (sent, viewed, signed, completed); compliance with eIDAS, ESIGN, UETA, GDPR, and HIPAA.`,
