    keywords: ["download document", "before signing", "signer", "signing link", "download button", "get started", "template gallery", "offline review", "esignature", "getsign", "monday.com"],
    body: `GetSign allows signers to download a document at any point before signing. Previously this was only available for documents generated within GetSign; it now works for documents accessed through the Template Gallery. There are two ways a signer can download: From the top navigation bar — the signer opens the signing link, locates the Download button in the top-right corner, and clicks it to save the document for offline review. From the opening dialog — when the document loads, a dialog appears and the signer finds the Download option beneath the Get Started button, clicks to download, and returns to sign when ready. Downloading is available before and alongside signing, so signers can review or print and come back to complete signing. Use cases: reviewing legal contracts, printing HR documents, assessing vendor agreements, reviewing proposals offline.`,
