    body: `Batch Signing sends one document to many recipients at once, each with their own personalized signing link; the system generates an individual copy for each signer, so you do not upload duplicate documents. Workflow: (1) Select multiple board items that need the same document signed. (2) Ensure the template or file is pinned to each selected item. (3) Configure an automation in monday.com's Automation Center based on a status column change (e.g., "Send for Signature"). (4) Update the status to the configured label to automatically generate personalized signing links. (5) Monitor completion in real time via board status updates. Capabilities: each signer receives a unique, secure link; documents can use fields mapped from the board (name, department, pricing); signature status updates automatically; only a single document upload per item is needed regardless of recipient count; works with monday.com native automation triggers. Compliance: legal audit trail, GDPR and HIPAA compliant. Included with no separate add-on fee for existing subscribers.`,
