    body: `What is GetSign? A document automation and e-signature app for monday.com; generate documents from board data, send for secure signature, track progress, and store everything in the monday workflow. Free plan or trial? A 14-day free trial with full premium access; afterward a free plan with document generation and basic e-signature. Generate from board data? Yes, using board items and sub-items; insert dynamic tables, auto-fill fields, and filter sub-items by status, priority, or owner. Send for e-signature? Yes, to single or multiple signers with legally binding e-signatures; define signing sequence and add signing fields; activity is tracked on the board. Track status? Yes, real-time trail showing when documents are viewed, signed, or awaiting action, plus a full audit log. Upload templates and edit? Template gallery supports DOCX and PDF; DOCX is editable in the integrated editor with smart field insertion. Forms and payments? Build forms with text boxes, dropdowns, checkboxes; collect payments via Stripe during signature. Branding? Upload logos and personalize signing emails. Storage? Signed documents save automatically to the relevant item's files column. Security? Complies with GDPR, HIPAA, and global signature standards with data encryption.`,
