    body: `GetSign integrates with monday.com to send contracts and collect signatures without leaving the platform. Step 1 - Install and access: install GetSign from the marketplace, open the item view of your sales pipeline board, and click "Add New Template" to upload your contract file. Step 2 - Enable signature collection: toggle on "Signature Collection" and select the column where signed contracts will be stored (e.g., "Signed Contract File"). Step 3 - Configure email delivery: in the GetSign Email Delivery section, enter the sender name and email, then complete verification. Step 4 - Add signature placeholder: click "Edit" in the document section to open the editor, drag the Signature field to the desired location, then save and close. Step 5 - Send: click Send to email the contract, or use "Generate Link"/"Copy Link" for manual sharing; track status within the board. Step 6 - Automatic updates: once signed, the signed document is automatically uploaded to the designated column and the status updates. Features: email automation for delivery and reminders, real-time tracking, automatic file storage, reusable contract templates.`,
